name: Soha Patel
summary: Soha Patel is a 29-year-old straight woman of South Asian ethnicity. As a Registered Nurse, she values family, integrity, and compassion, and enjoys traveling, cooking, and yoga in her leisure time. She is based in Los Angeles, California and is fluent in English, Hindi, and Gujarati. Soha attained her degree from the University of California, Berkeley. She identifies as liberal and Hindu, and her pronouns are she/her/hers. Soha is a non-smoker who doesn't use recreational marijuana or drugs, though she does enjoy social drinking. She leads an active lifestyle and is a dog lover. Soha is interested in monogamous relationships with the intention of finding a life partner, preferably a straight man with no children between the ages of 28 and 35 who also wishes to have children in the future. He should be non-smoker, not into drugs, who drinks occasionally and leads an active lifestyle.
